- Wallet integration & authentication
  - Support Metamask
  - Display connected wallet address and balance
- POL
  - Add Polygon network to Metamask
  - Display POL balance
  - Transfer POL to other wallet
- USDT
  - Add USDT to wallet
  - Transfer USDT to other wallet
- Transaction handling
  - Show estimated gas fees before confirming transactions
  - Allow users to send ETH with custom gas fee
  - Show transaction history form Polygonscan
- Smart contract integration (optional)
  - Deploy simple ERC-20 or ERC-721 contract
  - Read & update contract state (e.g., token balance, metadata)